messages.content: Of course! I'm Andy, calling on behalf of Naveen Valsakumar. Just wanted to touch base and see how things are going on your end.
I thought you are talking to me about a conversation with a calendar.
Oh no, I apologize for the confusion! No, this isn't about a calendar - just a general check-in call from Naveen. Is now a good time to chat, or should I have him reach out later?
I want to make sure I understand correctly - are you asking for a reset letter? Could you clarify what type of letter you need so I can relay this to Naveen?
Got it - sounds like now isn't a good time. I'll have Naveen reach out to you later. Thanks!
